My children go to Dr. Michelle since they were 2 years old. We absolutely adore her.
Dr. Kimura is an excellent dentist and wonderful with children. My kids love to go to her office for check up and honestly they can not wait when is the next appointment especially my 5 years old son.
Thank you so much Dr. Michelle for being a great doctor and beautiful person.
All the Best!

originalText.text: Awesome!!! That's all I can say about Dr. Kimura & her professional staff. I have 2 children (4 & 3) & they are both very shy. Dr. Kimura & her staff went above & beyond to make them feel comfortable for their visit. We live on the East side & make the hike up to the Upper West Side just so that my kids can be seen by Dr. Kimura. I highly recommend them.
